nodes.title: Florida received a test backlog from Quest Diagnostics

description.description: On September 1, 2020, the Florida Department of Health [announced](http://www.floridahealth.gov/newsroom/2020/09/090120-1112-covid19.pr.html) that Quest Diagnostics had reported nearly 75,000 backlogged tests dating as far back as April.

childMarkdownRemark.html: On September 1, 2020, the Florida Department of Health announced that Quest Diagnostics had reported nearly 75,000 backlogged tests dating as far back as April.

description.description: Florida started reporting hospitalizations of people with a “primary diagnosis of COVID-19.”
